                  = [5;10]</font></tt></p>
            <p>Now multiply<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b>A</b><span
                class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>by<span
                class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b><i>x</i></b><span
                class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>by
